OL,3,CVillage People frontman Victor Willis
OL,4,Cdies, aged 74
OL,6,FFrontman of 70s pop band Village
OL,7,FPeople, Victor Willis, has died aged
OL,8,F74, after being diagnosed with a
OL,9,F"short but aggressive illness".
OL,11,FWillis was the lead singer and
OL,12,Ffounding member of the disco pop group
OL,13,Fknown for hits such as Y.M.C.A and Go
OL,14,FWest.
OL,16,FThe band announced his death on social
OL,17,Fmedia, saying they were "profoundly
OL,18,Fsad to announce the death of Victor
OL,19,FWillis," and that he had a "short but
OL,20,Faggressive illness".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
