OL,3,CVillage People frontman Victor Willis
OL,4,Cdies, aged 74
OL,6,FVictor Edward Willis was born in
OL,7,FDallas, Texas in 1951. He was
OL,8,Fsurrounded by music from a young age
OL,9,Fand sang in his father's Baptist
OL,10,Fchurch.
OL,12,FAfter performing in musicals and
OL,13,Freleasing some solo albums, he met
OL,14,FFrench disco and dance producer
OL,15,FJacques Morali and songwriter Henri
OL,16,FBelolo.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
