OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782902882
OL,3,CVillage People frontman Victor Willis
OL,4,Cdies, aged 74
OL,6,FThe pair owned Can't Stop Productions,
OL,7,Fand were working with a band called
OL,8,Fthe Ritchie Family who needed backing
OL,9,Fsingers for their new album called
OL,10,FAfrican Queen.
OL,12,FAfter meeting Willis, they hired him
OL,13,Ffor the job then eventually formed a
OL,14,Fnew musical project in 1977, called
OL,15,FVillage People.
OL,17,FRecognised globally for their distinct
OL,18,Ffancy dress and disco dance moves,
OL,19,FWillis was remembered for his
OL,20,Fpoliceman and naval officer outfits.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
