OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782902882
OL,3,CVillage People frontman Victor Willis
OL,4,Cdies, aged 74
OL,6,FThe six-man band produced
OL,7,Finternational hits in the late 70s
OL,8,Flike, In the Navy, and, Macho Man,
OL,9,Fwhich are still played in nightclubs
OL,10,Fand discos nearly half a century after
OL,11,Ftheir release.
OL,13,FThe music of Village People has also
OL,14,Fbeen used in the political landscape,
OL,15,Fas President Donald Trump has been
OL,16,Fknown to blast the anthem and dance to
OL,17,FY.M.C.A at his rallies.
OL,19,FIn March, a social media trend saw
OL,20,FIranians dancing to the song during
OL,21,Fthe US airstrikes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
