PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782902882
OL,3,CVillage People frontman Victor Willis
OL,4,Cdies, aged 74
OL,6,FPosting on Facebook on March 3, Victor
OL,7,FWillis said: "I think it's really cool
OL,8,Fthat Iranians would use my song to
OL,9,Fcelebrate a possible change in their
OL,10,Fcountry.
OL,12,F"Hopefully peace will come soon to the
OL,13,Fpeople of Iran."
OL,15,FVillage People toured Europe in May
OL,16,Fthis year and even sang happy birthday
OL,17,Fto the United States Secretary of
OL,18,FState, Marco Rubio.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
