OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782902882
OL,3,CVillage People frontman Victor Willis
OL,4,Cdies, aged 74
OL,6,FThey performed at the 2026 FIFA World
OL,7,FCup draw at an arts centre in
OL,8,FWashington.
OL,10,FThe band are still releasing music,
OL,11,Fand in 2024 the band announced a new
OL,12,Fsingle called, Goddess of Love.
OL,14,FVictor Willis' wife Karen said his
OL,15,Fdeath was a "great loss" and requested
OL,16,Fprivacy at this time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
